This is a fork of boxroom, special flavoured.

### CHANGES
 * google chrome frame
 * jquery
 * no fancy jquery effects
 * xhtml doctype
 * packed gems
 * clean config files
 * Rails 2.3.4
 * maybe autodetection for apache upload progress module
 * maybe jPlayer
 * voting
 * calendar

### INSTALL

 1. git clone git://github.com/boof/rockflu.git
 2. # configure your datebase
 3. # configure boxroom in config/initializers/boxroom.rb
 4. mkdir uploads # or whatever
 5. rake gems:build
 6. # start application in thin, mongrel, whatever ...
 7. # launch your browser and visit your local rockflu
 8. # create admin
 9. # ...
